   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "68a4899d-9b96-452d-9d89-10b93fc0c974",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Subsetting the top 75% "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 86,
   "id": "62d390a0-73f7-4f73-877c-31fa29d662c5",
